[[File:Patrick skolgund.JPG|thumb|right|140px|Patrick Skoglund <br>PLEASE check whether this is the right person]]'''Patrick Skoglund''' (born 1967 in [[Uppsala]]) is a [[Civilekonom]] (MBA), who was, between 2007 and 2014, the Managing Director of Sandvikenhus AB, [[Sandviken Municipality]]'s [[public housing]].

From 2008-2011 he was chairman of Sandvikens Stadsutveckling (now Marknadsplats Sandviken), a business association.

