'''Gracia Putri Raemawasti''' (born December 5, 1986 in [[Blitar]], [[East Java]]) is Indonesian public figure and journalist. She was the winner of Puteri Indonesia (Miss Indonesia Universe) 2007 from [[East Java]].<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20070821075401/http://www.antara.co.id/arc/2007/8/4/putri-raemawasti-raih-gelar-putri-indonesia-2007/ Putri Raemawasti Raih Gelar Putri Indonesia 2007] at Antara.co.id</ref> She has attended the Institut Teknologi Sepuluh Nopember, Surabaya, majoring in industrial engineering.

==Miss Universe 2008==
Raemawasti represented [[Indonesia]] at the [[Miss Universe 2008]], but was unplaced. At the Miss Universe, she was the first Miss Indonesia to wear a two-piece bathing suit rather than the usual [[maillot]] one piece during the final presentation show.

